descriptor.short_desc: Women’s Wellness Herbal Tea Tisane - 100gm loose tea
descriptor.long_desc: Everybody knows how comforting a hot cup of tea is during menstruation, and a tea that has been particularly made to relieve PMS is the icing on the cake. For Her women's care herbal tea has the appropriate combination of ingredients for all the strong women out there to help you lessen uncomfortable cramps and nausea while also boosting your vigor and happiness. A normal, healthy cycle is supported by ayurvedic herbs, which also lessen bloating and discomfort of any kind. This tea is a great choice for women's health because it contains powerful herbs including Cinnamon, Ginger, Licorice, Fennel, Turmeric, Chamomile, Red Raspberry, Chest Tree Berries, and other natural herbs.
